{"tid":2157094,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"送首詩比巴塞 : 天長地久有時盡 此恨綿綿無絕期","createTime":"2020-08-14T21:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T21:44:04.000Z","uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a855a6a972fed238a08f08c4300bf7b737f2360","tid":2157094,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:22:20.000Z","msg":"作者: 白居易"},{"pid":"fedf968d6c652991a5546b172b22a1d161fbccbb","tid":2157094,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:24:05.000Z","msg":"六軍不發無奈何<br />\n宛轉蛾眉馬前死<br />\n花鈿委地無人收<br />\n翠翹金雀玉搔頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7e01e55da0cd3427a2ad6c93ae396b1d07085f","tid":2157094,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:31:22.000Z","msg":"詩。<br />\n綺美，瑰奇。<br />\n明月夜，落花時。<br />\n能助歡笑，亦傷別離。<br />\n調清金石怨，吟苦鬼神悲。<br />\n天下只應我愛，世間唯有君知。<br />\n自從都尉別蘇句，便到司空送白辭。"},{"pid":"18915cc964d17c2626070335c8a29322a4313bff","tid":2157094,"uid":35589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:32:42.000Z","msg":"八居二"},{"pid":"bf1b1572eaf08f3e357883dbd359d033590af834","tid":2157094,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18915cc964d17c2626070335c8a29322a4313bff","tid":2157094,"uid":35589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:32:42.000Z","msg":"八居二"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e134063d1d802f00bc96460ce061fc8512900dc","tid":2157094,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:39:43.000Z","msg":"美詩"},{"pid":"bdf38a7458898ce3e60dbc82cf9b83dd84b9f50d","tid":2157094,"uid":301668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18915cc964d17c2626070335c8a29322a4313bff","tid":2157094,"uid":35589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:32:42.000Z","msg":"八居二"},"citedB